title: Chemical Requirements
text: 5 Chemical Requirements

title: Notch Toughness Requirements
text: 7 Notch Toughness Requirements

title: Notch Toughness Requirements -> Notch Impact Testing
text: 7.1 Notch Impact Testing

title: Notch Toughness Requirements -> Notch Impact Testing

title: Annex A (informative) -> A.5 Control of the Application and Removal of the APl Monogram
text: The APl Monogram may be applied at any time appropriate during the production process but shall be removed in accordance with the licensee's API Monogram marking procedure if the product is subsequently found to be out of conformance with any of the requirements of the applicable APl product specification(s) and/or standard(s) and API Monogram Program.
